Bloodline Affinity			KEY:Trait ~ Bloodline Affinity					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Bloodline Affinity]			PRETEMPLATE:1,Voidkin		SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:Your black fur and melanistic complexion is the result of an ancient bloodline that runs through your veins that you may or may not be aware of. Regardless, you manifest unusual powers as a result of your heritage. Your sorcerer level is considered to be 1 level higher when determining the effects of your 1st-level bloodline power.
Exuberant					KEY:Trait ~ Exuberant							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Exuberant]					PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:Your lively performances help to improve the morale of anyone who experiences them. Once per day, when you use a spell or special ability to provide a morale bonus to an ally, you may improve that morale bonus by +1 for 1 round.
Inspired Artisan				KEY:Trait ~ Inspired Artisan						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Inspired Artisan]				PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You have a passion for the arts and are particularly skilled in a particular vocation. Select 1 Craft or Perform skill. You gain a +1 trait bonus on checks made with that skill.																																													MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SKILL|Craft%|Profession%		BONUS:SKILL|%LIST|1
Kitsune Loyalty				KEY:Trait ~ Kitsune Loyalty						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Kitsune Loyalty]				PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You never go back on your word and you are unquestionably devoted to your friends and allies. You gain a +1 trait bonus on saving throws against charm and compulsion effects.																																														ASPECT:SaveBonus|+1 on saves vs. charm and compulsion effects
Mysticism					KEY:Trait ~ Mysticism							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Mysticism]					PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You have learned to tap into your inner wellspring of magical power. Once per day when you cast a spell or spell-like ability, you can treat your caster level as 1 higher than your actual caster level. Additionally, increase your maximum age at each category after Youth (including your maximum age) by 10 years each time you have selected the Magical Tail feat. Adjust your aging bonuses and penalties according to your new age category.
Neighborly					KEY:Trait ~ Neighborly							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Neighborly]					PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You grew up in a kitsune community surrounded by supporting friends and family. When using the aid another action, you grant your ally a +3 bonus instead of a +2 bonus.
Omen of Greatness				KEY:Trait ~ Omen of Greatness						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Omen of Greatness]				PRETEMPLATE:1,Voidkin		SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:When you were born, your brilliant, white fur was decreed to be an omen of greatness. As a result, your word holds great weight with other kitsune. You receive a +1 trait bonus on Bluff, Diplomacy, and Intimidate checks when dealing with kitsune.
One Step Ahead				KEY:Trait ~ One Step Ahead						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ One Step Ahead]				PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You constantly scheme, to stay ahead of your adversaries. You gain a +1 dodge bonus to your AC against attacks of opportunity.																																																						ASPECT:CombatBonus|+1 dodge bonus to your AC against vs. of opportunity
Prankster					KEY:Trait ~ Prankster							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Prankster]					PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You spent your days constantly getting in and out of trouble as a youth. You quickly learned that the best way to avoid repercussions from your pranks was to leave before you were ever noticed. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Stealth checks and Stealth is always a class skill for you.																												BONUS:SKILL|Stealth|1|TYPE=Trait			CSKILL:Stealth

Blessed Artisan (Inari Okami)		KEY:Trait ~ Blessed Artisan			NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.ReligionTrait				PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.ReligionTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Blessed Artisan]			PREDEITY:1,Inari Okami		SOURCEPAGE:p.28	DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You were trained in the art of sword crafting by the followers of Inari Okami from a young age. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Craft (weapons) checks.																																																		BONUS:SKILL|Craft (Weapons)|1|TYPE=Trait
Touch of Prosperity (Inari Okami)	KEY:Trait ~ Touch of Prosperity		NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.ReligionTrait				PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.ReligionTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Touch of Prosperity]			PREDEITY:1,Inari Okami		SOURCEPAGE:p.28	DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Inari Okami has gifted you with the power to help others prosper. You gain the following spell-like ability: 2/dayâ€”guidance (caster level 1st). If you have levels in a class that can cast guidance, your caster level for this spell-like ability is equal to that class's level. 																													SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=2|CASTERLEVEL=1|Guidance

Involuntary Shapechange			KEY:Drawback ~ Involuntary Shapechange				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback						PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassDrawbackRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drawback ~ Involuntary Shapechange]		PRERACE:1,Kitsune			SOURCEPAGE:p.28				DESC:You are unable to maintain proper control over your shapeshifting abilities while impaired, causing features such as your ears, legs, tail, or tail to revert to their true form. While using change shape, you lose the +10 racial bonus on Disguise checks granted by change shape while you are sickened or nauseated. Additionally, each time you become sickened, nauseated, or suffer any amount of ability damage or ability drain while using change shape you must reroll your Disguise check and use the worse result. You cannot select this drawback if you possess the naturalize alternate racial trait.

