Disguise Aid			KEY:Kitsune Star Gem Trick ~ Disguise Aid			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		SOURCEPAGE:26	DESC:You can expend one use from a kitsune star gem when you use change shape in order to treat your Disguise check result as a natural 20.
Focus Component			KEY:Kitsune Star Gem Trick ~ Focus Component		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		SOURCEPAGE:26	DESC:You can add a kitsune star gem to a spell or spell-like ability as an additional focus component, expending one use from it in order to increase the spell's caster level by +1.
Skillful Edge			KEY:Kitsune Star Gem Trick ~ Skillful Edge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		SOURCEPAGE:26	DESC:You can expend one use from a kitsune star gem as a swift action in order to gain a +4 insight bonus on the next skill check you make. This check must be made within 1 round or this bonus is lost.
Star Strike				KEY:Kitsune Star Gem Trick ~ Star Strike			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		SOURCEPAGE:26	DESC:You can expend one use from a kitsune star gem as a free action when you use Arcane Strike in order to increase the bonuses received by +1 for the feat's duration.
Magical Recharge			KEY:Kitsune Star Gem Trick ~ Magical Recharge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		SOURCEPAGE:26	DESC:You can expend one use from a kitsune star gem as a standard action to restore one charge to a wand (if you have Craft Wand) or a staff (if you have Craft Staff).
